    narrator_der_fuchs_text_1: "Fox, you may open your eyes now.<br>Choose a person.<br>I will show you whether they or one of their two neighbors is a werewolf.<br>If one is a werewolf, I give a thumbs up.<br>If no one is a werewolf, I give a thumbs down<br>and you lose your ability.<br>(The fox points to a person)<br>(Narrator shows whether there is a werewolf in the trio or not)<br>Fox, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_der_fuchs_text_2: "Fox, you may open your eyes now.<br>Choose a person.<br>I will show you whether they or one of their two neighbors is a werewolf.<br>If one is a werewolf, I give a thumbs up.<br>If no one is a werewolf, I give a thumbs down<br>and you lose your ability.<br>(The fox points to a person)<br>(Narrator shows whether there is a werewolf in the trio or not)<br>Fox, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_der_grosse_boese_werwolf_text: "(call only every other night)<br>Big Bad Werewolf, open your eyes.<br>Choose a second victim you want to kill that night.<br>(The Big Bad Werewolf points to a victim)<br>Big Bad Werewolf, now close your eyes.",
    narrator_der_obdachlose_text_1: "Homeless man, you can open your eyes now.<br>Choose a person with whom you would like to spend the night.<br>If the person is eaten by the werewolves in the night, you will die too.<br>You are not allowed to sleep with one person for two nights.<br>(The homeless man points to a person)<br>Homeless man, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_der_obdachlose_text_2: "Homeless man, you can open your eyes now.<br>Choose a person with whom you would like to spend the night.<br>If the person is eaten by the werewolves in the night, you will die too.<br>You are not allowed to sleep with one person for two nights.<br>(The homeless man points to a person)<br>Homeless man, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_der_stotternde_richter_text: "Judge, you may open your eyes now.<br>Show me a secret little sign that you will make<br>if a second vote is to take place today.<br>(The judge and the narrator agree on a secret sign)<br>Judge, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_der_verbitterte_greis_text: "Embittered old man, you can open your eyes now.<br>Divide our group into two smaller, equal groups.<br>(E.g. dark hair and light hair)<br>If one of these groups is eliminated and you are still alive, you win.<br>(The embittered old man makes two groups)<br>You can close your eyes again.",
    narrator_der_weisse_werwolf_text: "(only call up every other night)<br>White werewolf, you may now open your eyes.<br>Which of your werewolf colleagues do you want to kill?<br>(The white werewolf points to a werewolf)<br>White werewolf, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_der_wolfshund_text: "Wolfhound, you can open your eyes now.<br>I hold up the two hands, the right hand means werewolf<br>and the left hand means villager.<br>(Narrator holds up both hands)<br>Decide what you want to be.<br>(The wolfhound points to one of the hands)<br>Wolfhound, close your eyes now.",
    narrator_die_drei_brueder_text: "Brothers, you can open your eyes now.<br>Look at each other so that you recognize each other.<br>(The three brothers look at each other)<br>Brothers, please close your eyes again.",
    narrator_die_zwei_schwestern_text: "Sisters, you can open your eyes now.<br>Look at each other so that you recognize each other.<br>(The two sisters look at each other)<br>Sisters, please close your eyes again.",
    narrator_dieb_text: "Thief, you may now open your eyes.<br>I now hold the two remaining roles in my hand.<br>You can now swap your role with one of the two roles or keep your role.<br>(Narrator holds up the two remaining cards)<br>If you keep your role, you remain a villager.<br>If you want a new card, point to it.<br>(Narrator takes away the card that the thief doesn't want)<br>Thief, close now your eyes.",
    narrator_floetenspieler_text_1: "Flute player, you can now open your eyes.<br>Now choose two people you would like to enchant with your music.<br>(The flute player points to two people)<br>Flute player, now close your eyes.<br>I'm now tapping the enchanted ones.<br>(Narrator goes around and taps the enchanted ones)<br>You can now wake up the enchanted ones<br>and use hand signals to discuss who the one is The flute player is.<br>If the flute player has enchanted everyone, he wins.<br>You who are enchanted can now close your eyes.",
    narrator_floetenspieler_text_2: "Flute player, you can now open your eyes.<br>Now choose two people you would like to enchant with your music.<br>(The flute player points to two people)<br>Flute player, now close your eyes.<br>I'm now tapping the enchanted ones.<br>(Narrator goes around and taps the enchanted ones)<br>You can now wake up the enchanted ones<br>and use hand signals to discuss who the one is The flute player is.<br>If the flute player has enchanted everyone, he wins.<br>You who are enchanted can now close your eyes.",
    narrator_fuchs_no_werewolf: "None of the three are werewolves. You have lost your ability.",
