    narrator_gaukler_text_1: "Juggler, you can now open your eyes.<br>I am now holding the three roles selected for you in my hand.<br>You can now decide which role you would like to play for this night.<br>(The juggler points to one of the roles)<br>Juggler, close your eyes.",
